          "requestedAt": "2026-05-19T20:06:51.684Z",
          "description": "Increase default FAB size from 40px to 50px and make it configurable: add button.size (number, px) to DebuggerButtonConfig. Validate as a finite positive number; default 50. Reject 0, negative, non-finite, and non-number values with a [debugger-pro-plus-3000]-prefixed error.",
          "requestedBy": "task-request-changes",
          "status": "implemented",
          "implementedAt": "2026-05-19T20:13:09.435Z",
          "filesChanged": [
            "src/config/types.ts",
